summary: there’s been some speculation that marvel edited out someone between bruce and rhodey (which is likely they’ve edited trailers...
caption:
there’s been some speculation that marvel edited out someone between bruce and rhodey (which is likely they’ve edited trailers in the past)

so, my prediction is that it’s CAPTAIN MARVEL

and for whatever reason, they don’t want us to know she’s with them yet because she hasn’t appeared in any trailer thus far

and that means….

THEY ARE ALL LOOKING UP TO SEE TONY COMING BACK HOME!!!!!!!!

summary: Endgame
title: Endgame
body:
Iron Man #165

Simple enough, but enjoyable.

  • In this chapter of the ongoing story, Iron Man faces a series of traps while searching for a kidnapped friend.
  • An arrogant/overconfident villain watches in frustration while Tony figures out ways to escape each one.
  • Straightforward, but fun.
  • Denny O'Neil (7 of 49).
  • Luke McDonnell (4 of 37). 

6/10

Steve’s pretty sure that Tony wants to hide their relationship because he’s ashamed, that was pretty much presumed back in his day, and he’s fine with waiting, but sometimes he just want to show the world. He won’t, he can’t
